          <div class="cil-row" data-handle="luna.creates" data-followers="48000" data-stopping-power="92" data-staying-power="74" data-brand-cut-through="67" data-emotional-resonance="83">
            <span class="cil-rank">6</span>
            <span class="cil-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF2198, #F9BE00);">LC</span>
            <div class="cil-info">
              <span class="cil-handle">@luna.creates</span>
              <span class="cil-followers">48K followers</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cil-bar-wrap">
              <div class="cil-bar" data-score="92"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="cil-score">92</span>
            <div class="cil-hover-card">
              <div class="cil-emotions">
                <span class="cil-emo" style="background:#FF2198" title="Joy"></span>
                <span class="cil-emo" style="background:#54E42B" title="Excitement"></span>
                <span class="cil-emo" style="background:#F9BE00" title="Surprise"></span>
              </div>
              <span class="cil-overlap">Audience overlap: 8%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cil-callout" id="cil-callout">
          <span class="cil-callout-text" id="cil-callout-text">48K followers &rarr; #1 by stopping power</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cil-insight glass-card fade-up">
        <div class="cil-insight-icon">&#10022;</div>
        <div>
          <p class="cil-insight-text">The data tells a clear story: no single creator dominates every metric. @luna.creates stops the scroll, @creativemira makes the brand stick, and @nova.daily triggers the deepest emotional response &mdash; each at a fraction of the reach of @maxviral.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PILLAR 04: STRATEGY -->
  <section class="pillar-section pillar-strategy" id="pillar-strategy">
    <div class="pillar-inner">
      <div class="pillar-text">
        <span class="eyebrow fade-up">04</span>
        <h2 class="pillar-title fade-up">Strategy</h2>
        <p class="pillar-question fade-up">What is my story?</p>
        <p class="pillar-desc fade-up">Everything combined. Benchmarks against competitors, brand positioning from real audience data, and the emotional territory your brand owns &mdash; so your strategy is built on how people actually feel.</p>
        <a href="#final-cta" class="btn btn-outline fade-up">Explore Strategy &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-graphic fade-up">
        <svg class="strategy-icon" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="strategy-grad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#007AFF"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#00A0FF"/>
            </linearGradient>
            <filter id="strategy-glow">
              <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="6" result="blur"/>
              <feMerge><feMergeNode in="blur"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
            </filter>
          </defs>
          <!-- Crosshair / target -->
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="140" fill="none" stroke="url(#strategy-grad)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.12"/>
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="100" fill="none" stroke="url(#strategy-grad)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.18"/>
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="60" fill="none" stroke="url(#strategy-grad)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.25"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="50" x2="200" y2="350" stroke="url(#strategy-grad)" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.15"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="200" x2="350" y2="200" stroke="url(#strategy-grad)" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.15"/>
          <!-- Center dot -->
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="18" fill="url(#strategy-grad)" opacity="0.7" filter="url(#strategy-glow)"/>
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="6" fill="#fff" opacity="0.9"/>
          <!-- Floating metric dots -->
          <circle cx="260" cy="120" r="8" fill="url(#strategy-grad)" opacity="0.4"/>
          <circle cx="310" cy="180" r="6" fill="url(#strategy-grad)" opacity="0.3"/>
          <circle cx="140" cy="280" r="7" fill="url(#strategy-grad)" opacity="0.35"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="160" r="5" fill="url(#strategy-grad)" opacity="0.25"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detail: Strategy — Brand Territory Reframe -->
  <section class="btr-section" id="detail-strategy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="btr-header fade-up">
        <span class="pill pill-blue">BRAND TERRITORY REFRAME</span>
        <h2 class="section-headline">Where does your brand <span class="text-gradient">stand?</span></h2>
        <p class="btr-subtitle">Click a territory to reframe the benchmark. Your brand strength shifts depending on who you&rsquo;re competing against.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="btr-card glass-card fade-up" id="btr-card">
        <!-- Territory Pills -->
        <div class="btr-pills" id="btr-pills">
          <button class="btr-pill active" data-territory="premium">vs Premium Leaders</button>
          <button class="btr-pill" data-territory="innovation">vs Innovation Leaders</button>
          <button class="btr-pill" data-territory="authenticity">vs Authenticity Leaders</button>
          <button class="btr-pill" data-territory="trust">vs Trust Leaders</button>
          <button class="btr-pill" data-territory="sustainability">vs Sustainability Leaders</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Gauge -->
        <div class="btr-gauge-wrap" id="btr-gauge-wrap">
          <svg class="btr-gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 300 180" id="btr-gauge-svg">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="btr-arc-grad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#007AFF"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#00A0FF"/>
              </linearGradient>
              <linearGradient id="btr-arc-bg-grad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.06)"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.06)"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <!-- Background arc -->
            <path id="btr-arc-bg" class="btr-arc-bg" d="" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.06)" stroke-width="16" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- Filled arc -->
            <path id="btr-arc-fill" class="btr-arc-fill" d="" fill="none" stroke="url(#btr-arc-grad)" stroke-width="16" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- Benchmark line (dashed) -->
            <line id="btr-benchmark-line" class="btr-benchmark-line" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="0" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
            <text id="btr-benchmark-label" class="btr-benchmark-label" x="0" y="0">Benchmark</text>
          </svg>
          <!-- Score display -->
          <div class="btr-score-display">
            <div class="btr-score-number" id="btr-score-number">0</div>
            <div class="btr-score-label">Brand Strength Score</div>
            <div class="btr-delta" id="btr-delta">
              <span class="btr-delta-arrow" id="btr-delta-arrow">&uarr;</span>
              <span class="btr-delta-text" id="btr-delta-text">+6 above benchmark</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Funnel Metrics -->
        <div class="btr-metrics" id="btr-metrics">
          <div class="btr-metric" data-metric="awareness">
            <div class="btr-metric-value" id="btr-m-awareness">0%</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-label">Awareness</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-delta" id="btr-md-awareness"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="btr-metric" data-metric="favorability">
            <div class="btr-metric-value" id="btr-m-favorability">0%</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-label">Favorability</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-delta" id="btr-md-favorability"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="btr-metric" data-metric="consideration">
            <div class="btr-metric-value" id="btr-m-consideration">0%</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-label">Consideration</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-delta" id="btr-md-consideration"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="btr-metric" data-metric="purchaseIntent">
            <div class="btr-metric-value" id="btr-m-purchaseIntent">0%</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-label">Purchase Intent</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-delta" id="btr-md-purchaseIntent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="btr-metric" data-metric="brandMemory">
            <div class="btr-metric-value" id="btr-m-brandMemory">0%</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-label">Brand Memory</div>
            <div class="btr-metric-delta" id="btr-md-brandMemory"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ellie Insight -->
      <div class="btr-insight glass-card fade-up" id="btr-insight">
        <div class="btr-insight-icon">&#10022;</div>
        <div>
          <p class="btr-insight-text" id="btr-insight-text">Your brand over-indexes on premium perception. This is your strongest territory &mdash; lean into it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AUDIENCE INTELLIGENCE — THE CROWN -->
  <section class="audience-section" id="audience">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="audience-header">
        <span class="eyebrow fade-up">THE BIGGER PICTURE</span>
        <h2 class="audience-title fade-up">Data says X. Humans feel Y.<br>
          <span class="text-gradient-audience">Ask Ellie.</span></h2>
      </div>

      <!-- ASK ELLIE PROMPT BAR -->
      <div class="ellie-prompt glass-card fade-up">
        <div class="ellie-prompt-inner">
          <div class="select-group">
            <label>Brand</label>
            <select id="aud-brand">
              <option value="" disabled selected>Choose a brand</option>
              <option value="nike">Nike</option>
              <option value="netflix">Netflix</option>
              <option value="spotify">Spotify</option>
              <option value="cocacola">Coca-Cola</option>
              <option value="bbc">BBC</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="select-group">
            <label>Goal</label>
            <select id="aud-goal">
              <option value="" disabled selected>Choose a goal</option>
              <option value="awareness">Increase brand awareness</option>
              <option value="launch">Launch in a new market</option>
              <option value="consideration">Boost brand consideration</option>
              <option value="purchase">Drive purchase intent</option>
              <option value="affinity">Build brand affinity</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary ellie-prompt-btn" id="aud-ask-btn">
            <span class="ellie-icon">&#10022;</span> Ask Ellie
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MAP (bigger: ~70vh) -->
    <div class="audience-map-wrap">
      <canvas class="audience-map-canvas" id="audience-canvas"></canvas>
      <div class="audience-tooltip" id="aud-tooltip"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- ELLIE INSIGHT CARD (hidden, shown after query) -->
      <div class="ellie-insight-card glass-card" id="aud-insight-card">
        <div class="ellie-insight-card-header">
          <span class="ellie-icon">&#10022;</span> Ellie
        </div>
        <div class="ellie-insight-card-body" id="aud-insight-body"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- FOOTER: Dual-mode legend -->
      <div class="audience-footer fade-up">
        <div class="audience-legend" id="aud-legend">
          <!-- Default legend (emotion-based) -->
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-default"><i style="background:#FF2198"></i>Joy</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-default"><i style="background:#F9BE00"></i>Surprise</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-default"><i style="background:#10A8B7"></i>Trust</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-default"><i style="background:#54E42B"></i>Excitement</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-default"><i style="background:#007AFF"></i>Focus</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-default"><i style="background:#8F21A1"></i>Curiosity</span>
          <span class="aud-leg-divider aud-leg-default"></span>
          <span class="aud-leg-note aud-leg-default">Dot size = attention level</span>
          <!-- Query legend (benchmark-based, hidden by default) -->
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-query" style="display:none"><i style="background:#54E42B"></i>Above benchmark</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-query" style="display:none"><i style="background:#F9BE00"></i>Growth opportunity</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-query" style="display:none"><i style="background:#FF2198"></i>Whitespace / easy capture</span>
          <span class="aud-leg aud-leg-query" style="display:none"><i style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)"></i>Deprioritize</span>
          <span class="aud-leg-divider aud-leg-query" style="display:none"></span>
          <span class="aud-leg-note aud-leg-query" style="display:none">Dot size = audience size</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#final-cta" class="btn btn-primary">See Ellie in Action &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section" id="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="final-cta-content fade-up">
        <h2>Your next campaign doesn't have to be a guess.</h2>
        <p>See what your media spend actually does — what's working, what's not, and what to change.</p>
        <div class="final-cta-buttons"><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book a Demo</a><a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">Talk to Our Team</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <svg width="180" height="28" viewBox="0 0 180 28" fill="none">
          <circle cx="10" cy="14" r="9" fill="url(#gGf)"/><circle cx="26" cy="14" r="9" fill="url(#gPf)"/><circle cx="42" cy="14" r="9" fill="url(#gOf)"/>
          <text x="56" y="20" fill="white" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-weight="700" font-size="15">Element Human</text>
          <defs><linearGradient id="gGf" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#54E42B"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#10A8B7"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="gPf" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FF2198"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8F21A1"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="gOf" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F9BE00"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F60000"/></linearGradient></defs>
        </svg>
        <p class="footer-tagline">Know what's working.<br>Fix what's not.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col"><h4>Platform</h4><a href="#pillar-measurement">How Ellie Works</a><a href="#">Science</a></div>
      <div class="footer-col"><h4>Use Cases</h4><a href="#">Campaign ROI</a><a href="#">Creator Optimization</a><a href="#">Creative Testing</a><a href="#">Channel Comparison</a></div>
      <div class="footer-col"><h4>Company</h4><a href="#">About</a><a href="#">Contact</a><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a><a href="#">Terms</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom container"><p>&copy; 2026 Element Human. All rights reserved.</p></div>
  </footer>

  <script src="js/homepage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
